    "That may lead the model to overfit, besides being sensitive to noise spikes (e.g., when the rewards are stochastic).",
    "Therefore, they proposed a stochastic sampling method that combines greedy prioritization and uniform random sampling by defining the sample probability based on a transition's priority value.",
